        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# 3 — Pipelines d'annotation Spark NLP {background-color=\"#065A82\"}\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {style=\"color: #CADCFC; font-size: 0.9em;\"}\n",
        "DocumentAssembler · SentenceDetector · Tokenizer · Normalizer\n",
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## 3 — Pipeline Spark NLP\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.columns}\n",
        "::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n",
        "**5 étapes dans l'ordre :**\n",
        "\n",
        "| # | Annotateur | Rôle |\n",
        "|---|---|---|\n",
        "| 1 | `DocumentAssembler` | Mise en forme |\n",
        "| 2 | `SentenceDetector` | Découpage phrases |\n",
        "| 3 | `Tokenizer` | Tokens |\n",
        "| 4 | `Normalizer` | Nettoyage |\n",
        "| 5 | `Normalizer` | Minuscules |\n",
        "\n",
        ":::\n",
        "::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n",
        "```python\n",
        "document  = DocumentAssembler()\\\n",
        "  .setInputCol(\"text\")\\\n",
        "  .setOutputCol(\"document\")\n",
        "\n",
        "nlp_pipeline = Pipeline(stages=[\n",
        "  document, sentence,\n",
        "  tokenizer, normalizer\n",
        "])\n",
        "\n",
        "annotated = (\n",
        "  nlp_pipeline\n",
        "  .fit(corpus_sdf\n",
        "    .repartition(N_CORES, \"filename\"))\n",
        "  .transform(corpus_sdf)\n",
        ")\n",
        "```\n",
        ":::\n",
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# 4 — Analyse Stylométrique {background-color=\"#065A82\"}\n",
